data.title: Biriyani
data.desc: Spicy flavourful chicken dum cooked with layers of aromatic basmati rice, caramelised onion.

data.title: Chilli Chicken
data.desc: Chilli chicken is a sweet, spicy & slightly sour crispy appetizer made with chicken, bell peppers, garlic, chilli sauce & soya sauce.

data.title: Paneer Tikka
data.desc: Paneer Tikka is a North Indian appetizer where chunks of paneer are marinated in spiced yogurt and grilled in a Tandoor, a traditional clay oven.

data.title: Paneer 65
data.desc: Paneer 65 is a spicy South Indian appetizer made with Paneer aka Indian cheese, flour, spices and herbs like curry leaves.

data.title: Chilli gobi
data.desc: A fusion dish, chilli gobi is crispy, spicy, slightly sweet and sour tasting. The cauliflower florets are batter coated, deep fried.
